<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Birthday Scheduler</title>
    <style>
        body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          background: url('https://source.unsplash.com/1600x900/?birthday,celebration') no-repeat center center/cover;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          display: flex;
          justify-content: center;
          align-items: center;
          height: 100vh;
          text-align: center;
          color: #dddec7;
        }
    
        .container {
          background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
          padding: 30px 40px;
          border-radius: 10px;
          width: 90%;
          max-width: 500px;
          box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
    
        h2 {
          font-size: 2rem;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    
        form {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 15px;
        }
    
        .form-group {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
        }
    
        .form-group label {
          margin-bottom: 5px;
          font-weight: bold;
        }
    
        .form-group input {
          width: 100%;
          padding: 10px;
          border: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
          font-size: 1rem;
        }
    
        .btn {
          padding: 10px 20px;
          font-size: 1rem;
          color: white;
          background: #ff4081;
          border: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
          cursor: pointer;
          transition: background 0.3s;
        }
    
        .btn:hover {
          background: #e6005c;
        }
      </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Schedule a Birthday Surprise!</h1>
        <p>Make your loved ones feel special by scheduling a birthday reminder for them.</p>
        <a href="/create" class="btn">Get Started</a>
    </div>  
</body>
</html>